OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering showers easing away, then a
OL,7,Fdry night with clear spells. Overnight
OL,8,Ftemperatures rather fresher than of
OL,9,Flate in northern parts, especially in
OL,10,Frural spots. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,13,Fwarm or very warm for many again on
OL,14,FSaturday. Cooler near coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,17,Fmore unsettled and cooler during the
OL,18,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,19,Ffalling nearer normal for the time of
OL,20,Fyear. Becoming breezy with outbreaks
OL,21,Fof occasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
